						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ••••••Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription records that this flower garden was a gift of a certain Padiyātāṉ Mādaṉ <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Kulōttuṅgachōḻak Kāṅgēyaṉ.</p>						

						<p>This record on the grounds of paleography may be assigned to the 14th century A.D. </p>						

